textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value CTS_STATUS (\S+)
Value POLICY (\S+)
Value PEER_DEVICE (\S+)
Value AUTHENTICATION (\S+)
Value SHARED_SECRET (Configured|Not Configured)
Value SGT (\d+)

Start
  ^Interface:\s+${INTERFACE}$$
  ^\s+CTS Status:\s+${CTS_STATUS}$$
  ^\s+Policy:\s+${POLICY}$$
  ^\s+Peer Device:\s+${PEER_DEVICE}$$
  ^\s+Authentication:\s+${AUTHENTICATION}$$
  ^\s+Cisco_Shared_Secret:\s+${SHARED_SECRET}$$
  ^\s+SGT:\s+${SGT}$$ -> Record
